  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Category</strong>: Clan<br /><strong>Prerequisite</strong>: Nanaya Clan, level 8+<br /><strong>Description</strong>: Moving with precision, each step calculated, making next to no noice, undetectable and acrobatic, that is the style of the Nanaya assassins. You gain the following benefits:</p><ul><li>You can walk at your full movement speed while hidden.</li><li>You can walk on walls and roofs without spending chakra, and your wall walking speed becomes equal to your normal walking speed. You must end your movement on the floor or you start to fall.</li><li>Twice per rest, when you would be forced to make a dexterity or strength saving throw. You may spend a reaction to make the save at advantage. On a success, you can cast a Nanaya clan hijutsu with enough range to reach the triggering creature, with a casting time of an action, as part of the same reaction.</li></ul>",
